This repository contains a collection of SQL practice projects and query exercises.
Each project was created to develop and demonstrate skills in data extraction,
cleaning, transformation, and analytical problem‑solving.

## Contents
- SQL query exercises
- Data cleaning and transformation
- Joins, subqueries, and CTEs
- Aggregations and window functions
- Practice datasets

## Tools Used
- SQL Server / MySQL / PostgreSQL
- SQL Management Studio / Azure Data Studio
- Sample CSV / database tables
